同埋呀涂生話唔想個制裁影響香港經濟呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 販民都冇心攬炒嘅<br />\n<br />\n叫人加速 但又開聽證會係咩玩法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最撚叻仔係你啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"a767469b76734894c87083503d79bda46ee3d288","tid":1565374,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T14:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fe44501ba2e4d8508ec172053f84e549db31191","tid":1565374,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac92719e52807655c61afa6c23c168347dbebfd","tid":1565374,"uid":27467,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:49:56.000Z","msg":"話你無腦驚你嬲，繼續做你冷氣軍師，自己香港自己救"},{"pid":"a1a165d33266568383927546b4ed4c00482409d0","tid":1565374,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"why not both?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d58dbd51aea33d3a3f167ba72193d472cb0d945","tid":1565374,"uid":24133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:08:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17d3af2d145501b21dbc733ae9add9e72e388d6","tid":1565374,"uid":169801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29e6c57b149a66c0f90c92bc6f8568b0fc73db21","tid":1565374,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T06:22:47.000Z","msg":"我知道大家見到個標題應該好撚嬲，不過有啲野我都係要講。<br />\n<br />\n呢刻唔應該唱香港國歌，係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唱美國國歌加揮美國國旗</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n唱香港國歌只係加快香港去死。一班無議價能力既人，無論數量幾多，唱到本地國歌唱到上九重天都係對極權毫無威脅。但一班人唱起一個願意伸出援手既美國國歌時先係對共產極權的惡夢。<br />\n<br />\n你地呢幾日唱得咁開心，真係唔覺有問題? 入曬全港九新界商場居然無人出黎譴責，投訴妨礙生意?  連黑警都唔出黎守下商場門口? 然後又有一班愛國團體出黎同你地鬥唱，俾你地鬥贏埋。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根本係港共、財團同民間愛國社團夾埋</span></strong>，連翻既喜悅就係想我地<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沉醉係政治娛樂</span></strong>入面，忘記向美國求援。 <br />\n<br />\n尋日同今日分別有美國議員反對推行人權法同將香港剔除係貿易協議內(本身侵侵都將香港剔除貿易戰之內)，呢兩件事證明人權法依然有暗湧，我地唔可以忽略。<br />\n<br />\n大家可能會問，美國真係見到我地民意??? 係，佢地真係見到。<br />\n<br />\n今日既事:<br />\n茶黨始創人 Michael Johns 在 Twitter 公開推文說「Resist Beijing, Liberate Hong Kong.」<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/michaeljohns/status/1171076245876088832?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmichaeljohns%2Fstatus%2F1171076245876088832%3Fs%3D21&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=3287bef1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmichaeljohns%2Fstatus%2F1171076245876088832%3Fs%3D21&h=2f79e0e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/michaeljohns/status/1171076245876088832?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n民主黨參議員 Dick Durbin 今日在 Twitter 公開支持通過《香港人權及民主法案》，並且指要盡快通過（as soon as possible）。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senatordurbin/status/1172202951894589440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatordurbin%2Fstatus%2F1172202951894589440&d=mymTsZ9rb3gbearwAuc4QRR1GjkmqS0yYYF7Sw2QOJY%3D&h=050412ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenatordurbin%2Fstatus%2F1172202951894589440&h=ae107c68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senatordurbin/status/1172202951894589440</a><br />\n<br />\n美國眾議夠16人'聯署香港人權及民主法。等17號復會再推上去。<br />\n<br />\n說話都呢到，可以的話今晚以及未來日子繼續見到唱美國國歌加揮美國國旗。<br />\n<br />\n我知道有人會唔中意我既說話，你地中意唱乜就唱乜。我無野講。<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T03:19:41.000Z","msg":"今時今日仲屌唱歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">知唔知點解你會比人屌，唔係人地鐘意嘉年華，係兄弟爬山呀</span></span>，有人掉汽油彈，有人示威，有人唱歌，有人人鏈，各自爬山，唔阻對方，唔鬧對方，覺得邊樣啱自己就參加邊樣，吸引最多既人參與運動，簡單來講做咩都好過企係度咩都唔做等運到，佢又無要你強制參加，你有咩好路數咪自己宣傳，吸引人來囉，係要屌人d活動搞到你負皮灑更加無人理你"}]}